QuestData.Title: Promontory Point
QuestData.Description: We need to get this information up to Captain Taylor on Promontory Point! He's out there to the northwest with Erunak Stonespeaker and the Earthen Ring.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Captain Taylor on Promontory Point in Vashj'ir.
QuestData.RewardText: That's very disturbing news, but I believe our Earthen Ring friends here have a plan.$B$BAnd now that you're here....
